Field Documentation

uint8_t ReloadOption

Velocity Timer Reload Option, should be:

  • QEI_TIMERRELOAD_TICKVAL: Reload value in absolute value
  • QEI_TIMERRELOAD_USVAL: Reload value in microsecond value
